{"tid":2358360,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔：『最近天氣開始轉涼了！』","createTime":"2021-01-08T05:33:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-08T07:49:37.000Z","uid":71767,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ee154464d46dbd466beaa6038e678cf7e6162eb9","tid":2358360,"uid":71767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T05:33:09.000Z","msg":"十五度，西班牙人穿大衣、戴手套；西伯利亞人作日光浴。<br />\n十度，法國人開暖氣；西伯利亞人在花園裡種花。<br />\n五度，義大利人發不動車子，西伯利亞人開敞篷車遊街。<br />\n零下五度，加州人凍斃了；西伯利亞人在戶外烤肉。<br />\n零下十度，英國人開暖氣；西伯利亞人開始穿長袖。<br />\n零下五十度，北極熊撤離北極；西伯利亞軍隊延後冬季野外求生訓練，等待真正的冬天到來。<br />\n零下一百八十三度，食物中的微生物死亡；西伯利亞牛隻抱怨酪農的手太冰。<br />\n零下兩百七十三度，原子停止活動；西伯利亞人終於說：『老天，外面好冷！』<br />\n連登仔：『最近天氣開始轉涼了！』"},{"pid":"3e3d9bbf08c23b3ddd5b11d4132344631e0c6cba","tid":2358360,"uid":369679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T05:34:22.000Z","msg":"入來就係為咗睇潮文"},{"pid":"d436c74e6ec591937ac8903f7581deebcb237769","tid":2358360,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T05:37:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kgy45MC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKgy45MC.png&h=72674705&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c262054f770791a6738632bdcbbf4f95d0e42bbf","tid":2358360,"uid":388788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d436c74e6ec591937ac8903f7581deebcb237769","tid":2358360,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T05:37:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kgy45MC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKgy45MC.png&h=72674705&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T07:49:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}